# 🎙️ Speech Analyzer with Whisper + IBM Watsonx LLM

This project demonstrates AI-powered audio and language processing using **OpenAI Whisper** for speech recognition and **IBM Watsonx LLM** for text summarization.

---

## 🚀 Features
- 🎧 Convert speech to text using Whisper
- 🧠 Summarize key points with IBM Watsonx LLM
- 🌐 Web apps built with Gradio
- 💡 Modular and beginner-friendly structure

---

## 🗂️ Project Files
- `simple_llm.py` → Basic text generation with IBM Watsonx
- `simple_speech2text.py` → Basic Whisper speech-to-text
- `speech2text_app.py` → Gradio transcription app
- `speech_analyzer.py` → Complete Whisper + LLM summarizer
- `requirements.txt` → Dependencies
- `setup_instructions.txt` → Environment setup
- `README.md` → Project overview

---

## ⚙️ Setup

```bash
python3 -m venv my_env
source my_env/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

▶️ Run

python speech_analyzer.py
